Attributes.description: Nursing practice to integrate and consolidate professional nursing knowledge, skills and competencies in the care of infants, children, youth and their families.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: All of NURS 300, NURS 310, NURS 321, NURS 322, NURS 330, NURS 352.
Attributes.coreq: Co-reqs: NURS 346 and one of NURS 323, NURS 401.
